 joined Steven Van Zandt's one-time-only supergroup to cover a song that would many years later inspire one of his own.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Cover Me&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Cover Me", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/cover-me/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/admin-ajax-2026-06-10T144915.948.jpg?fit=1174%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/admin-ajax-2026-06-10T144915.948.jpg?fit=1174%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/admin-ajax-2026-06-10T144915.948.jpg?fit=1174%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/admin-ajax-2026-06-10T144915.948.jpg?fit=1174%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/admin-ajax-2026-06-10T144915.948.jpg?fit=1174%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=1050%2C600 3x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 3659, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/1972/01/25/roll-of-the-dice-when-you-dance/", "url_meta": {"origin": 6921, "position": 5}, "title": "When You Dance", "author": "Ken", "date": "January 25, 1972", "format": false, "excerpt": "Bruce wrote and performed \"When You Dance\" with The Bruce Springsteen Band long before Southside Johnny covered and released it, and Bruce's early guitar-jam version is an unreleased gem that belong's in every fan's collection.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;BSB&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "BSB", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/bsb/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/whendance.jpg?fit=1024%2C1024&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/whendance.jpg?fit=1024%2C1024&ssl=1